        <zone h='27263' id='25' name='Sheet 13' w='29421' x='1105' y='47368' />
        <zone h='24158' id='26' name='Sheet 9' w='39895' x='1158' y='75000' />
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='20579' id='29' type-v2='text' w='55316' x='42105' y='77947'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='20'>KEY INSIGHTS</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='14'>1</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='14'>.churn rate is far higher here than for one- or two-year contracts, making contract type the strongest lever for retention.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='14'>2</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='14'>.churn is heavily concentrated in the </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='14'>0-12 month tenure bucket</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='14'>, then drops steadily as tenure increases.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='14'>3</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='14'>.customers on automatic payments (bank transfer/credit card) are far more loyal, suggesting a push toward auto-pay could reduce churn.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='14'>4.</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='14'>The highest-risk segment is Month-to-month + Electronic check (1,850 customers, 53.7% churn rate)  this is the single largest group to target first, accounting for $77,316 in at-risk revenue, or 55.6% of the total $139,131 revenue at risk.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
